

TRIGGERING “BUY“ OR
“SELL“ BUTTONS

When Logic Query 1 (Direction) is completed and result
displayed in unique popup window (the one you developed last night- v0.0.0.0.6)
THEN

IF condition is met in:
Sub_protocol_ID                 66 activate “BUY” button

                                67 activate “SELL” button

                                68 activate “BUY” button

                                69 activate “SELL” button”

                                70 activate “SELL” button

                                71 activate “BUY” button

                                72 activate “BUY” button

                                73 activate “SELL” button

